{"tha-ap198:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap198:0.2":"Tamalapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap198:0.3":"Kisalayapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap198:1.1":"“Nagare dvaravatiya, ","tha-ap198:1.2":"malavaccho mamam ahu; ","tha-ap198:1.3":"Udapano ca tattheva, ","tha-ap198:1.4":"padapanam virohano. ","tha-ap198:2.1":"Sabalena upatthaddho, ","tha-ap198:2.2":"siddhattho aparajito; ","tha-ap198:2.3":"Mamanukampamano so, ","tha-ap198:2.4":"gacchate anilanjase. ","tha-ap198:3.1":"Annam kinci na passami, ","tha-ap198:3.2":"pujayoggam mahesino; ","tha-ap198:3.3":"Asokam pallavam disva, ","tha-ap198:3.4":"akase ukkhipim aham. ","tha-ap198:4.1":"Buddhassa te kisalaya, ","tha-ap198:4.2":"gacchato yanti pacchato; ","tha-ap198:4.3":"Taham disvana samvijim, ","tha-ap198:4.4":"aho buddhassularata. ","tha-ap198:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap198:5.2":"pallavam abhiropayim; ","tha-ap198:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap198:5.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap198:6.1":"Sattatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap198:6.2":"eko ekissaro ahu; ","tha-ap198:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap198:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap198:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap198:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap198:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap198:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kisalayapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap198:9.1":"Kisalayapujakattherassapadanam chattham. "}